{0 Octez-protocol-025-PsGXQmSv-libs: octez protocol 025-PsGXQmSv libraries}

This is a package containing some libraries related to the Tezos 025-PsGXQmSv protocol.

It contains the following libraries:

- {{!module-Tezos_025_PsGXQmSv_test_helpers}Tezos_025_PsGXQmSv_test_helpers}: Protocol testing framework
- {{!module-Tezos_025_PsGXQmSv_test_migration}Tezos_025_PsGXQmSv_test_migration}: Protocol migration testing checks
- {{!module-Tezos_agnostic_baker_025_PsGXQmSv}Tezos_agnostic_baker_025_PsGXQmSv}: Protocol specific library for the Agnostic Baker
- {{!module-Tezos_baking_025_PsGXQmSv}Tezos_baking_025_PsGXQmSv}: Base library for `tezos-baker/accuser`
- {{!module-Tezos_baking_025_PsGXQmSv_commands}Tezos_baking_025_PsGXQmSv_commands}: Protocol-specific commands for baking
- {{!module-Tezos_client_025_PsGXQmSv}Tezos_client_025_PsGXQmSv}: Protocol specific library for `octez-client`
- {{!module-Tezos_dal_025_PsGXQmSv}Tezos_dal_025_PsGXQmSv}: Protocol specific library for the Data availability Layer
- {{!module-Tezos_layer2_utils_025_PsGXQmSv}Tezos_layer2_utils_025_PsGXQmSv}: Protocol specific library for Layer 2 utils
- {{!module-Tezos_protocol_plugin_025_PsGXQmSv}Tezos_protocol_plugin_025_PsGXQmSv}: Protocol plugin
- {{!module-Tezos_protocol_plugin_025_PsGXQmSv_registerer}Tezos_protocol_plugin_025_PsGXQmSv_registerer}: Protocol plugin registerer
- {{!module-Tezos_smart_rollup_025_PsGXQmSv}Tezos_smart_rollup_025_PsGXQmSv}: Protocol specific library of helpers for `tezos-smart-rollup`
- {{!module-Tezos_smart_rollup_layer2_025_PsGXQmSv}Tezos_smart_rollup_layer2_025_PsGXQmSv}: Protocol specific library for `tezos-smart-rollup`
